 in fact }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs10 satisfied by linking the documents of 27 October 2010 and 20 April 2011}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid4143269\cs10  }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs10 pursuant to the doctrine of joinder of documents as discussed by Chesterman J in }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\i\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs10 Todrell Pty Ltd v Finch (No1)}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\i\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid14834779\cs10 ,}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\i\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs24\super\chftn{\footnote\pard\plain\itap0\s25\tx607\fi-607\aspalpha\aspnum\pararsid15228119\ltrpar\li607\lin607\ri0\rin0\ql\faauto\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs20\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs20\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5596866\cs24\super \chftn }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs20\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5596866\cs10  \tab [2008] 1 Qd R 540}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs20\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid13331875\cs10 .}}}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid13188185\cs10  is indeed }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid1986503\cs10 sustainable }{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid13188185\cs10 in the current circumstances}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs10 ;}{\rtlch\alang1025\afs20\ltrch\fs24\f0\lang3081\langnp3081\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid15228119\cs10\par}\pard\plain\itap0\s44\aspalpha\aspnum\pararsid159